        <div id="artwork-image">
            <a href="..\/images\/31658_4173269.jpg" class="enlargement-link enlargement-link-183006"><img src="../images/31658_4173271.jpg" alt="Fragment from Christ Carrying the Cross: Mourning Virgin" title="Jean Hey, known as the Master of Moulins
